        <updateDate>2020-03-03T17:10:46Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>Travel and Tourism for All Act</b></p> <p>This bill requires the National Council on Disability, with respect to the travel, tourism, and hospitality industries, to conduct a review and report on the progress of the implementation of standards related to accessibility of public accommodations and commercial facilities for persons with a disability.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
